This is almost 700 points.

18
00:03:53,410 --> 00:03:56,720
God Nan Xi, you are so, so, so awesome!

19
00:03:56,800 --> 00:04:00,520
I can foresee
how we can take over Binhai University.

20
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,530
Nan Xi, you are extraordinarily great.

21
00:04:05,610 --> 00:04:09,320
Rui, you're the only one
