22
00:04:10,540 --> 00:04:12,640
-Okay, I'll check it out.
-Check earlier and you'll be at ease.

23
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,810
That's right!
This year's paper was easy.

24
00:04:14,890 --> 00:04:16,050
You will definitely be fine.

25
