26
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,269
You will definitely score more than 450.

27
00:04:19,349 --> 00:04:21,950
What do you mean
by, "Even Cheng Erluo scored 420?"

28
00:04:22,030 --> 00:04:25,270
I put in a lot of effort revising, okay?

29
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:29,980
Rui has always been working harder
than me,

30
00:04:30,060 --> 00:04:33,190
which is why it shouldn't be a problem
for her to score over 450 points.

31
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,360
That's right.

32
00:04:39,470 --> 00:04:41,770
Well, then, I will call it now.

33
