Mathematics, 90 points.

42
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,700
It's okay, Math was difficult this year.

43
00:05:19,780 --> 00:05:22,240
It's really good to be able
to just pass it, really!

44
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:24,100
-Ninety...
-There are more, there are more.

45
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:26,090
English, 105 points.

46
00:05:26,170 --> 00:05:27,580
Yes! Counter attack!

47
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,940
Steady, steady, steady!

48
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:30,900
One more, one more.

49
